      • getNode

        public Node getNode()
        Called from the NativeNodeContainer constructor. Implementations instantiate a new instance of a node but don't load its settings yet. The latter should be done in NodeContainerPersistor.loadNodeContainer(java.util.Map, org.knime.core.node.ExecutionMonitor, org.knime.core.node.workflow.WorkflowPersistor.LoadResult) as this method is called from a not fully instantiated NativeNodeContainer (reduce API calls during construction).
